Action.name: Change_flow_fraction
Action.scriptCode:
var r = new Random();
return r.NextDouble()*3/5 + 0.5;

Action.name: Update_CP1_FP
Action.scriptCode:
double NewTimeToRefuel = TimeToRefuel - ( CP1_Deg_Start-  Start_NormOps_Time);
return  1 - Math.Exp( -Pump_Degrad_Shape*( Math.Exp(Pump_Degrad_Scale*NewTimeToRefuel) - 1 ) );
